<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/complete-fix.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <div class="step-card">
                <h3>Step 4: Admission Confirmation</h3>
                <p>Upon successful completion of the interaction/test and verification of documents, parents will be
                    notified of the admission status. You can then proceed with fee payment to confirm the admission.
                </p>
            </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            </section>

            <section class="eligibility-documents-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="card-row">
                        <div class="card">
                            <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Pre-Nursery:</strong> Child should be 3+ years as of 31st March of the
                                    admission year.
                                </li>
                                <li><strong>Nursery:</strong> Child should be 4+ years as of 31st March of the admission
                                    year.</li>
                                <li><strong>Class I onwards:</strong> Age-appropriate admission as per CBSE guidelines.
                                </li>
                                <li>For higher classes, a transfer certificate (TC) from the previous recognized school
                                    is mandatory.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <h2>Required Documents</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Attested photocopy of Birth Certificate (for Pre-Nursery to Class I).</li>
                                <li>Transfer Certificate (TC) from the previous school (for Class II onwards).</li>
                                <li>Photocopy of Aadhar Card of the child and parents.</li>
                                <li>Latest passport-size photographs of the child (4 copies) and parents (2 copies
                                    each).</li>
                                <li>Previous academic year's report card (for Class II onwards).</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="important-dates-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Important Dates (Tentative)</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Admission Form Availability:</strong> January 15, 2026 onwards</li>
                        <li><strong>Last Date for Form Submission:</strong> February 28, 2026</li>
                        <li><strong>Interaction / Test Dates:</strong> March 1-15, 2026</li>
                        <li><strong>Admission Confirmation & Fee Payment:</strong> March 15-31, 2026</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><em>Please note that these dates are tentative and may be subject to change. Kindly contact the
                            school office for the most current information.</em></p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="call-to-action">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Have Questions?</h2>
                    <p>Our admission counselors are ready to help you with any queries.</p>
                    <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button primary">Contact Admissions Office</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>